I"Q<p>Ballot papers have been sent to ‘eligible’ residents on Stepney’s <a href="https://estatewatch.github.io/estates/towerhamlets/clichyestate/">Clichy estate</a> despite the consultation on future options for their homes having been cancelled due to the Coronavirus crisis.</p>

